OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FITV News revealed details of the cuts
OL,7,Fjust over a week ago, sparking a
OL,8,Ffierce backlash from Labour MPs. In
OL,9,Fresponse to the leaked proposals, the
OL,10,Fgovernment have since scrapped plans
OL,11,Fto freeze Personal Independence
OL,12,FPayments (Pip) in 2026.
OL,14,FBut a major package of changes is
OL,15,Fstill expected, as the Chancellor
OL,16,Ftries to scrape savings together
OL,17,Fbefore her Spring Statement.
