OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FPip is a benefit designed to help
OL,7,Fpeople with a disability to pay for
OL,8,Fadditional costs, such as wheelchairs,
OL,9,Fcars, above average bills, carers, and
OL,10,Fspecialist equipment. It can be
OL,11,Fclaimed by people both in and out of
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,FAround 3.2 million people claim Pip -
OL,15,Fthat's up more than a million since
OL,16,F2019 - and is forecast to reach five
OL,17,Fmillion by 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
