OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FAs ITV News revealed, the government
OL,7,Fis still expected to cut the top rate
OL,8,Fof incapacity benefit, which currently
OL,9,Fsits at more than #800 a month.
OL,10,FIncapacity benefits give additional
OL,11,Fincome to people whose health limits
OL,12,Ftheir ability to work.
OL,14,FITV News also detailed how the basic
OL,15,Frate of Universal Credit paid to
OL,16,Fpeople in work or looking for work
OL,17,Fwill be raised, while the rate for
OL,18,Fthose judged unfit for work will be
OL,19,Fcut.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
