OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FThe government has announced the
OL,7,Fpackage of reforms will include giving
OL,8,Fdisabled people the "right to try"
OL,9,Femployment without the risk of losing
OL,10,Ftheir benefits.
OL,12,FHow much is the government hoping to
OL,13,Fsave?
OL,15,FThe tough decision to cut benefits
OL,16,Fcomes as Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,17,Fdesperately tries to find areas where
OL,18,Fshe can save money ahead of her Spring
OL,19,FStatement next week and the Office for
OL,20,FBudget Responsibility's official
OL,21,Fforecast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
