OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FIn their last forecast the OBR said
OL,7,FReeves had #10bn of headroom, but that
OL,8,Fappears to have been wiped out by
OL,9,Fglobal factors like Donald Trump,
OL,10,Fhigher borrowing costs, and weak
OL,11,Feconomic growth.
OL,13,FITV News reported Reeves was due to
OL,14,Fmake #6bn of savings through welfare
OL,15,Fcuts, but with the Pip freeze
OL,16,Fscrapped, there are now questions
OL,17,Fabout exactly how the sums will add up.
