OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FThe blanket Pip freeze would have been
OL,7,Feasy for the OBR to "score" ahead of
OL,8,Ftheir forecast next week, but the
OL,9,Fother changes are more complex in
OL,10,Fterms of measuring potential savings.
OL,12,FThe Resolution Foundation estimate
OL,13,Fcutting Pip by #5bn in 2029-30 by
OL,14,Fchanging the thresholds for support
OL,15,Fcould mean 620,000 people lose on
OL,16,Faverage #675 a month.
