OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FStarmer and his cabinet are targeting
OL,7,Fbenefits because the bill has rocketed
OL,8,Fin recent years, reaching #48 billion
OL,9,Flast year. It's forecast to continue
OL,10,Frising to #67 billion in 2029-30 ` a
OL,11,Flevel that would exceed the current
OL,12,Fschools budget and which the
OL,13,Fgovernment regards as unsustainable.
OL,15,FThe number of people in England and
OL,16,FWales claiming either sickness or
OL,17,Fdisability benefit has risen sharply
OL,18,Ffrom 2.8 million in 2019 to around
OL,19,Ffour million today.
