OL,6,FWhy is the government facing a
OL,7,Fbacklash over the changes?
OL,9,FA number of Labour MPs have made their
OL,10,Ffierce opposition to the plans clear
OL,11,Fbehind the scenes, with some reports
OL,12,Fsuggesting up to 100 are against the
OL,13,Fchanges.
OL,15,FLast week all Labour MPs were called
OL,16,Fin to Number 10 for briefings about
OL,17,Fthe cost of benefits, in an effort to
OL,18,Ftry and win them over.
