OL,3,CWhat key decisions is the government
OL,4,Cfacing over welfare?
OL,6,FSome Labour figures have come out
OL,7,Fpublicly and criticised the move -
OL,8,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,9,FBurnham urged "caution on how changes
OL,10,Fare made" in an an article for the
OL,11,FTimes.
OL,13,FBurnham said that Starmer is "right"
OL,14,Fand "the British state is not
OL,15,Fsustainable in its current form" but
OL,16,Fthe government should focus on helping
OL,17,Fpeople into work rather than simply
OL,18,Fcutting benefits.
